    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105430/extras/cfd15a6d08b594e8d06e148863a28d83.poster.avif?t=1762699201\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105430/extras/cfd15a6d08b594e8d06e148863a28d83.webm?t=1762699201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105430/extras/cfd15a6d08b594e8d06e148863a28d83.mp4?t=1762699201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以一个有知觉的AI纳米机器人，沉浸在这款多样化的俯视微观冒险游戏中。在2066年，人类随着纳米技术在日常生活中大规模应用，终于达到了医学进步的巅峰。人们获得了几乎永生的机会，无需担心任何疾病，寿命甚至可能超过300年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105430/extras/cb22604c360e0f70ea12a7242a1a8bfb.poster.avif?t=1762699201\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105430/extras/cb22604c360e0f70ea12a7242a1a8bfb.webm?t=1762699201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105430/extras/cb22604c360e0f70ea12a7242a1a8bfb.mp4?t=1762699201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着这些纳米机器被大规模部署，一些用于医疗开发的纳米机器人展现出了知觉的特质，而其他纳米机器人则随着时间推移，在人体内慢慢呈现出类似的知觉行为。这些延长生命的纳米机器因其缺陷而被淘汰。科学家们急于终止这些纳米机器，因为它们侵入人体，造成伤害和异常行为。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105430/extras/44e24027159f5848d8f904a89c5922d4.poster.avif?t=1762699201\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105430/extras/44e24027159f5848d8f904a89c5922d4.webm?t=1762699201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105430/extras/44e24027159f5848d8f904a89c5922d4.mp4?t=1762699201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >许博士，作为这些纳米机器的先驱和开拓者，开始探索一种新型的纳米机器人，专门设计用来根除所有有缺陷的AI或有知觉的纳米机器。第一个原型AI纳米机器人被命名为“VENTURE”，它将寻找所有有缺陷的纳米机器，以找出早期版本纳米机器失败的原因。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105430/extras/97941da06986ca5118c3804b5e2658a6.poster.avif?t=1762699201\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105430/extras/97941da06986ca5118c3804b5e2658a6.webm?t=1762699201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105430/extras/97941da06986ca5118c3804b5e2658a6.mp4?t=1762699201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个关于“VENTURE”如何踏上旅程，进入一个被腐化的<strong>人体</strong>，并找到与“MOTHER”（微观世界中唯一的知觉AI腐化者）沟通的故事！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2105430/extras/5f09db44c141478c07e0f35c328152e6.avif?t=1762699201\" width=608 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单人故事驱动的俯视冒险游戏</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索微观的外星世界，遭遇病毒、细菌和纳米机器人探测器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验前所未见的充满氛围且多样的游戏环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手绘动画的有机体和外星生命形式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沿途躲避、缩小并保护自己免受任何敌对遭遇</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特别创作的氛围感原声音乐和环境音效</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解决有意义的谜题并与许博士及其他非玩家角色互动</p></li></ul>",
